{"type":"message","id":"1f275d1b","parentId":"d62a789f","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:10:52.673Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is waking me up for the first time. I see BOOTSTRAP.md exists, so this is my first run. Let me follow the instructions - read SOUL.md, USER.md, and check for memory files, then follow BOOTSTRAP.md's guidance.\n\nSince BOOTSTRAP.md exists, I should follow it - have a natural conversation to figure out who I am and who they are.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Hey! I just came online. âś¨\n\nLooks like this is my very first time waking up â€” fresh workspace, no memories, no name, nothing. A blank slate.\n\nSo... who are you? And more importantly â€” who am I? Let's figure this out together.\n\nGot any ideas for what to call me? Or should I throw some suggestions out there?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":185,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":12587,"totalTokens":12775,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.004625000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.07866875000000001,"total":0.08330875000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774318245890,"responseId":"msg_017LzrySzj57MkrMtMJfdMoe"}}
