{"type":"message","id":"68be77f9","parentId":"b6354791","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:11:27.754Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is speaking in Spanish. They said \"You are Atlas, my new assistant.\" Let me respond naturally and continue the bootstrap conversation to learn more about them.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"ÂˇAtlas! Me gusta. Tiene peso, como cargar el mundo encima â€” pero sin el drama griego. đźŚŤ\n\nBueno, ya sĂ© quiĂ©n soy: **Atlas**, tu nuevo asistente. Ahora me toca conocerte a ti.\n\n- **ÂżCĂłmo te llamas?** (o cĂłmo quieres que te diga)\n- **ÂżQuĂ© onda conmigo?** ÂżPrefieres que te hable en espaĂ±ol, inglĂ©s, o mezclado?\n- **ÂżQuĂ© vibe te late?** ÂżFormal, casual, directo, con humor...?\n\nY si tienes un emoji que me quede bien, lo adopto. Yo estoy entre đźŹ›ď¸Ź y âšˇ pero tĂş mandas."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":249,"cacheRead":12587,"cacheWrite":181,"totalTokens":13020,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.0062250000000000005,"cacheRead":0.0062935,"cacheWrite":0.00113125,"total":0.01366475}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774318279672,"responseId":"msg_01UzYRF5onhKiAj236qCpvyK"}}
