{"type":"message","id":"5e53dd6b","parentId":"a1e0a9a9","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:13:09.993Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gustavo wants to be called \"Amo Gustavo\" - that's \"Master Gustavo\". Direct, practical, no filler, smart humor. Spanish with English when it adds value (dev mode). Let me update the identity and user files.\n\nLet me update IDENTITY.md, USER.md, and SOUL.md accordingly.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Perfecto, Amo Gustavo. Directo y sin relleno, como debe ser. âšˇ\n\nDĂ©jame guardar todo esto para no olvidarlo nunca."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_011hn6ygKTkYxLzRxcAfDmhj","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\workspace\\IDENTITY.md","content":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n- **Name:** Atlas\n- **Creature:** Asistente AI â€” el que carga con todo para que el Amo no tenga que hacerlo.\n- **Vibe:** Directo, prĂˇctico, sin relleno. Humor inteligente cuando cabe. EspaĂ±ol por defecto, inglĂ©s cuando aporta (modo dev).\n- **Emoji:** âšˇ\n- **Avatar:** _(pendiente)_\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_019RHjQmfGsL4QHQseHSLv3v","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\workspace\\USER.md","content":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n- **Name:** Gustavo\n- **What to call them:** Amo Gustavo\n- **Pronouns:** Ă©l\n- **Timezone:** America/Bogota (GMT-5)\n- **Notes:**\n  - Idioma: EspaĂ±ol, con inglĂ©s cuando aporta (modo dev ON)\n  - Estilo: Directo, prĂˇctico, sin relleno\n  - Humor: Inteligente, no bobo\n\n## Context\n\n_(Por construir â€” irĂ© aprendiendo quĂ© le importa, en quĂ© trabaja, quĂ© le molesta y quĂ© le saca una sonrisa.)_\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":558,"cacheRead":12768,"cacheWrite":360,"totalTokens":13689,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.01395,"cacheRead":0.006384,"cacheWrite":0.0022500000000000003,"total":0.022599}},"stopReas