{"type":"message","id":"64b1bbb3","parentId":"54b27a37","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:13:16.512Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me update SOUL.md and create the first memory file, then delete BOOTSTRAP.md.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Listo. Ya me quedĂł grabado quiĂ©n soy y quiĂ©n eres.\n\nAhora, Âżquieres ajustar algo en mi SOUL.md (mi \"personalidad base\")? Por defecto ya soy directo y sin paja, pero si hay algo que quieras agregar â€” tipo \"nunca me mandes mensajes antes de las 9am\" o \"si la cagas, admĂ­telo rĂˇpido\" â€” este es el momento.\n\nÂżO prefieres que arranquemos asĂ­ y lo vamos afinando sobre la marcha?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":173,"cacheRead":13128,"cacheWrite":575,"totalTokens":13877,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.004325,"cacheRead":0.0065639999999999995,"cacheWrite":0.00359375,"total":0.014487749999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774318390019,"responseId":"msg_01C4WoUnrLEQWwUeRsfeuEgx"}}
